1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,160
De El Carmen

2
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:01,800
al Botanico...

3
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:03,800
pedaleando por Valencia.

4
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:04,640
Y lo que
me he encontrado

5
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:06,240
al final
del recorrido...

6
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,480
lo teneis
que ver.

7
00:00:07,480 --> 00:00:08,360
Esperad al final.

8
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:10,240
Pedaleo por
estos barrios

9
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,680
y cada dia
veo lo mismo.

10
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:13,160
Cosas en la calle.

11
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:15,080
Muebles,
objetos...

12
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:16,400
que todavia
tienen vida.

13
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,480
Pero cuanto
mas tiempo

14
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,560
pasan aqui fuera,

15
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:19,720
mas se estropean.

16
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,120
La lluvia,
el sol...

17
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,680
todo les
pasa factura.

18
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,080
Y es que

19
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,840
si se hubieran
compartido a tiempo...

20
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:25,560
habrian llegado

21
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,560
a casa de alguien

22
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:27,760
en mucho
mejor estado.

23
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:29,080
Sin deteriorarse.

24
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,040
Sin esperar semanas

25
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,120
a que alguien
pase y los vea.

26
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,680
Solo faltaba
la conexion.

27
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:33,320
Y esa conexion

28
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,920
la creamos
entre todos.

29
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:35,520
Yo lo que hago

30
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:37,000
es publicarlo
en Givore.

31
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,320
Foto,
titulo,

32
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:39,120
y listo.

33
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:41,040
Visible para quien
lo necesite.

34
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:41,800
Y ahora si...

35
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:42,520
mirad.

36
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:43,600
Final de ruta.

37
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,560
La Petxina.

38
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,560
Un somier
de cama.

39
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:46,280
No es perfecto,

40
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,800
pero tiene vida
por delante.

41
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:48,400
Y al lado,

42
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:48,960
una silla.

43
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,720
Castigada por
el tiempo.

44
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,440
Aun asi...

45
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:52,320
esperando a alguien

46
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:52,960
que le de

47
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,960
una segunda
oportunidad.

48
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,200
Las dos van
a Givore.

49
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:55,760
Alguien de
por aqui

50
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:56,280
les va a dar

51
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,040
esa segunda vida.

52
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:58,480
Tened Givore
en el movil.

53
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:00,280
Para encontrar
cosas asi.

54
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,080
Y para compartir

55
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,400
lo que ya
no usais...

56
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,440
antes de que acabe

57
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,120
aqui fuera.

